message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a convolutional neural network approach for mandible segmentation in CT scans, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The application of this approach is in medical imaging (cs.MED) and specifically in the segmentation of mandibles, which involves the analysis of anatomical structures (cs.NEURON).
